org.ldaptive.ad

Class SecurityIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ldaptive.ad.SecurityIdentifier

  • public final class SecurityIdentifier
extends Object
    Class to represent an active directory SID. Provides conversion from binary to string and vice versa.
